Description: AllStar Link node monitoring dashboard (Supermon-ng)
 Supermon-ng provides a web UI for monitoring and controlling AllStar Link
 nodes: AMI integration, WebSocket live status, favorites, DVSwitch, and
 node status/weather updates via systemd timers.
 .
 This package installs the application under /var/www/html/supermon-ng,
 systemd units, and sudoers rules. Configure Apache/nginx separately
 (see /var/www/html/supermon-ng/docs/DEBIAN.md).
